
    Stormy Daniels' lawyer Michael Avenatti arrested

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                 Reuters
                
            
            
            Image caption
                
                    Michael Avenatti rose to prominence as lawyer to porn actor and director Stormy Daniels
                
            Michael Avenatti, lawyer for porn star Stormy Daniels in her suit against President Donald Trump, has been arrested on suspicion of domestic violence, police in Los Angeles say. TMZ website was first to report that the alleged victim was Mr Avenatti's estranged wife Lisa Storie-Avenatti.But her lawyers said she was not involved in the alleged incident, BuzzFeed News website reports.TMZ later also said the incident involved a different woman.Mr Avenatti is yet to make public comments on the issue.
    
        

    
      
              
